🚀 Getting Started
✅ Prerequisites
Node.js (v18+)
Java 17+ (Gateway uses 21 ⚠️)
MySQL
Redis
Kafka
RabbitMQ
MinIO
🔧 Start API Gateway
cd flashtix-gateway
./mvnw spring-boot:run

📌 Gateway runs before all services
📌 All requests go through gateway

🔧 Start Backend Services
cd flashtix-backend
./mvnw spring-boot:run
💻 Start Frontend
cd flashtix-frontend
npm install
npm run dev
📝 API Routing (via Gateway)

Instead of hitting services directly:

http://localhost:8080/api/...

Gateway routes to:

Auth Service
Event Service
Order Service
